<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heilbronn</head><p>Der Rat bestätigt den guten Leumund des Fritz N., der sich in Heilbronn niederlassen will, unter Berufung auf Bernhard Plattner und Peter Führenschild, Bürger zu Nürnberg.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_112" id="55r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_112_r3l18">Den von <expan>Heylprunn<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_112_r3l19"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von eins gſellen <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> genant fricʒ der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_112_r3l20">ſıch bey eẅch geſecʒt vnd ein weıb da <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hab / vnd als vns <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_112_r3l21">frıcʒ ſein ſache ercʒelt hat etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_112_r3l22">eẅr <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ wır ʒwen <expan>geſeſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>meıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> bey vns <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> mıt <expan>name<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_112_r3l23"><expan>meıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Bernhart<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Plattn<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex>n</expan> fürenſchılt für vns beſant vnd von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_112_r3l24">des <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> . f . <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> g </del> <expan>ernſtl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gefragt vnd <expan>v<ex>er</ex>höret</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . dıe <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vor </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_112_r3l26">vns geſagt daʒ <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> . f . Jn 
<add><ab facs="#facs_112_r3l25"><expan>beıd<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab></add> gedıent hab vnd niht args von Jm <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_112_r3l27">denn daʒ er ſıch redlıch vnd erberlıch bey Jn hab gehalten / Denn wo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_112_r3l28">wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> v<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> tyburcij </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_112" id="55r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den von <expan>Heylprunn<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                                  <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von eins
                                                gsellen <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, genant Fricz,
                                                der sich bey ewch geseczt und ein weib da
                                                  <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hab und als uns
                                                  <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> Fricz sein sache
                                                erczelt hat etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                                                wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                                                  <expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir zwen
                                                  <expan>gesess<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>meist<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns,
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> mit
                                                  <expan>name<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>meist<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Bernhart<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Plattn<ex>er</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Fürenschilt für uns
                                                besant und von des
                                                  <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>F<ex>ricz</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ernstl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gefragt und
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>höret</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Die
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vor uns gesagt, daz
                                                  <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>F<ex>ricz</ex></expan> in
                                                  <add><expan>beid<ex>en</ex></expan></add> gedient
                                                hab und niht args von im
                                                  <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, denn daz er sich
                                                redlich und erberlich bey in hab gehalten. Denn wo
                                                wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb
                                                  <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> v<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Tyburcii.</ab>
</div>
